Currently split 3 bed 2 bath and Mother in Law suite 2 bed 1 bath , Metal roof with 8 month old special screws. 4 year old A/C. New tile in master bedroom. Lot of upgrades throughout. Corner lot and very well located, near the ocean and in the center of Key West.
